---
title: Beef & Feta Meatballs with Carrot Couscous Tabbouleh & Yoghurt Dressing
description: The flavours of the Middle East are always a winner, and our tasty carrot couscous tabbouleh and yoghurt dressing are a case in point. Add beef and feta meatballs to the mix and you’ll be hard-pressed to stop your mouth watering while you cook!

*Unfortunately, this week's green beans were in short supply, so we've replaced them with broccolini. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
